org.apache.cordova.engine

Class SystemWebViewEngine

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.cordova.engine.SystemWebViewEngine
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CordovaWebViewEngine

    public class SystemWebViewEngine
extends java.lang.Object
implements CordovaWebViewEngine
    Glue class between CordovaWebView (main Cordova logic) and SystemWebView (the actual View). We make the Engine separate from the actual View so that: A) We don't need to worry about WebView methods clashing with CordovaWebViewEngine methods (e.g.: goBack() is void for WebView, and boolean for CordovaWebViewEngine) B) Separating the actual View from the Engine makes API surfaces smaller. Class uses two-phase initialization. However, CordovaWebView is responsible for calling .init().
